---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy · BitLife Online Fan Site">
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      Welcome to BitLife Online Fan Site (“we,” “us,” or “our”). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal information you share when visiting our site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We don’t require user registration or collect personally identifiable information (PII) to play the embedded game or view our content.
      However, like most websites, we do automatically collect some non-personal data for analytics:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> Your IP address, browser type, operating system, and pages viewed.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies & Tracking:</strong> We may use cookies (or similar local storage) to analyze site usage via a third-party analytics service (e.g., Google Analytics). These cookies do not identify you personally and can be disabled via your browser settings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We use aggregated, non-personal data solely for:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Monitoring site performance and improving user experience.</li>
      <li>Understanding which content and features are most popular.</li>
      <li>Diagnosing technical issues and preventing abuse.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We embed the BitLife Online game via an iframe from 
      <a href="https://bitlifeonline.github.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">bitlifeonline.github.io</a>. 
      We do not control any data that third-party sites or advertisers may collect. Please review their individual privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We (or our analytics provider) may set cookies to help us track anonymous usage metrics:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Necessary Cookies:</strong> Used to keep basic site functionality (e.g., session identifiers).</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Used to collect aggregate information about page visits and user flows.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      If you want to disable cookies, you can do so via your browser’s settings (e.g., Chrome → Settings → Privacy and security → Cookies and other site data). Disabling cookies may affect certain site features, but you can still access most content without them.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      Our site is intended for general audiences. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe your child has provided us with PII, please contact us so we can promptly delete it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">6. Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect data from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or data storage can be guaranteed 100% secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We may update this policy from time to time. The “Last updated” date below will reflect when changes were made. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 10, 2025</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please email us at  
      <a href="mailto:privacy@bitlifefansite.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">privacy@bitlifefansite.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
